com.musicbox.util

Class MusicRoomDataContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.musicbox.util.globalobject.GlobalObject
      • com.musicbox.util.MusicRoomDataContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MusicRoomDataContainer
extends GlobalObject
    This Class is used to store all Data of one music-room in one object and send it to startup clients or clients which are joining to this music-room.
    Author:
    David Wachs
